'''Amaḍal''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|tɛrabt]]: العالم, s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tfransist]]: ''le monde'') assaɣ ad as itussan atri n [[akal]] nɣ kawkab l'arḍ s tɛrabt, ar isdullu f tugt n tɣawsiwin zund amzruy d tamagit n afgan, Amaḍal waḥda a ḥ tlla tudrt n middn d imudar acku nttan a ḥ illa luksijin d waman d tignwit nɣ lɣilaf ljawwi s tɛrabt. Ar ttinin imassann awtay n umaḍal iga tt 4 kkuẓ id mlyar isggʷasn.

Amaḍal gis 6 n yigarawn : Agaraw Amlwi nɣ Pasifik, Agaraw Aṭlasi, Agaraw Ahindi, Agaraw Arkti, Agaraw Antarktik. Gis daɣ 6 n yimnẓawn : [[Asya]], [[Marikan|Tamrikt]], [[Tafriqt]], [[Urupa|Uruppa]], [[Uqyanusya]] d [[Antarktika|Tantarktit]].

Igarawn d waman dln 70,8% zɣ tjumma (superficie) n umaḍal. Tajumma nns 510.072.000 km<sup>2</sup> (yikilumitren imkuẓn). Gra-tsn 148.940.000 km<sup>2</sup> ig akal (28,8%) d 361.132.000 km<sup>2</sup> n waman. Amaḍal zdɣn-t 6,8 n yimlyaṛn n middn.

Llant ḥ umaḍal 194 n [[Timizar n Umaḍal|tmizar timzirgin]] (indépendantes).
